  "title": "BRANCH HEAD",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Mandate</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>The Branch Head is responsible for overseeing the branch’s marketing and sales initiatives, as well as managing its daily operations. This role supports the Commercial Banking Head in promoting and selling the Bank’s products and services, ensuring the branch meets I its financial and operational goals.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Duties &amp; Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>1.</strong> <strong>Business Development</strong></p>\n<p>Promote new deposit products, solicit new accounts, and cross-sell other banking products and services through proactive and strategic marketing efforts to meet financial targets.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>2.</strong> <strong>Sales &amp; Marketing Oversight</strong></p>\n<p>Supervise the branch’s overall marketing and sales operations, ensuring continuous improvement in service quality, customer engagement, transaction accuracy, and operational efficiency.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>3.</strong> <strong>Compliance &amp; Risk Management</strong></p>\n<p>Ensure strict adherence to bank policies, internal controls, regulatory requirements, and service standards across all branch activities.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>4.</strong> <strong>Personnel Management</strong></p>\n<p>Oversee staffing needs related to marketing, sales, customer service, and branch operations, ensuring optimal team performance.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>5.</strong> <strong>Team Development</strong></p>\n<p>Foster a positive and collaborative work environment, encouraging professional growth and development among branch personnel.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>6.</strong> <strong>Others</strong></p>\n<p>Perform additional duties as assigned to support branch and organizational objectives. </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
